%t A043281 Max[Length/@Split[IntegerDigits[#,7]]]&/@Range[100] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Mar 30 2016 *)
%o A043281 (PARI) A043281(n, b=7)={my(m,c=1); while(n>0, n%b==(n\=b)%b&&c++&&next; m=max(m, c); c=1); m} \\ _M. F. Hasler_, Jul 23 2013
